#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.139:4.5"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu appamatto ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti? "
msgstr "And how does a mendicant who is diligent develop and cultivate the noble eightfold path? "

msgctxt "sn45.139:4.6"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti nibbānaninnaṃ nibbānapoṇaṃ nibbānapabbhāraṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti nibbānaninnaṃ nibbānapoṇaṃ nibbānapabbhāraṃ. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion, which slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment. "

msgctxt "sn45.139:4.7"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu appamatto ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant who is diligent develops and cultivates the noble eightfold path.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.139:4.8"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

